author: Cory Shaffer, cleveland.com
title: Notre Dame College student gets jail time for stealing 650 pairs of women's underwear from dorm
text: A Notre Dame College student who stole more than 600 pairs of women's underwear from the laundry room in his dorm was sentenced Thursday to probation.
